 under the act bonus is calculated on the basis  of  the  employees  salary  and  the  profit  of  the  establishment    if  the establishment  says  that  it  has  not  earned  profit  it  would  decline  to  pay  bonus  what  is  the  solution  for  such  type  of  a  situation    in  mumbai  and  other  parts  of maharashtra there is a tendency among the corporate companies to make duplicate annual  reports  and  accounts  and  misguide  the  government  agencies    the  act provides that the central government may make rules to implement its provisions  i  am  glad  to  say  that  the  central  government  has  accepted  nine  demands  out  of twelve  submitted  by  the  trade  unions    the  hon  minister  says  that  the  bill  will come  into  effect  from  1st  april  2015    but  recently  we  have  received  the amendment it is made now 2014  we are going to pass it today  i do not know how it could be given retrospective effect  the hon minister may kindly explain this  i have no hesitation in supporting this bill     